item.title: CVE-2020-5030|2024-08-04T08:22:09.064Z -- ibm -- rational%20rhapsody%20model%20manager
item.description: IBM Jazz Foundation and IBM Engineering products are vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 193737.

item.title: CVE-2020-4964|2024-08-04T08:14:59.274Z -- ibm -- rational%20rhapsody%20model%20manager
item.description: IBM Jazz Team Server products contain an undisclosed vulnerability that could allow an authenticated user to present a customized message on the application which could be used to phish other users. IBM X-Force ID: 192419.
